    "The TREC (PM) dataset is a collection of data",
    "Table 13 Publicly available codes from related studies References 200 Page 48 of 60 and queries used in the TREC Precision Medicine track.",
    "It typically consists of queries that are clinically motivated questions, resembling the information needs of physicians.",
    "It also consists of a large set of documents that the search algorithms use to find relevant information.",
    "These documents can include scientific articles, clinical trial reports, and other related medical texts."
  ]
